  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">GTLP Itau PY CL</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">- The Project will enhance access to long-term finance for farmers and SMEs, enabling Itau Paraguay&apos;s clients to undertake capital investments at longer tenors and competitive terms;
- Due to the maximum average sub-loan size of up to US$1 million, the facility will be 100% used to serve SMEs;
- The mobilization of resources from other DFIs into Paraguay will support and consolidate the improvement of the business climate experienced by the Country over the past few years.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC will provide a $40 million facility to Banco Ita&#xFA; Paraguay (Ita&#xFA; Paraguay) to be on-lent to small and medium enterprises (SMEs) and to Agricultural sector players in Paraguay. 

The Project will support an IFC existing client with a dominant position in the retail segment, but which intends to grow its SME portfolio. Furthermore, the Project represents an excellent opportunity for IFC to mobilize resources from other DFIs into Paraguay, not only reaching small farmers and Agri-SMEs which are key drivers of the economic activity in the country, but also generating a demonstration effect that will contribute to consolidate IFCs programmatic approach in the Country.</narrative>
  </description>
